/* NaOH brine.  The liquid-activity slot is the electrolyte model -- selected
   like any activity model (one word: pitzer).  The salt's ions + solubility live
   in NaOH.dat (called by name); nothing chemical is re-typed here.  Self-contained:
   components copied into constant/components/. */
components       ( water NaOH );
activityModel    { model pitzer; }
equationOfState  { model idealGas; }
